{"title":"春蚕——茅盾先生周年祭","authors":["徐新杰"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":3,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"春蚕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——茅盾先生周年祭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"徐新杰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在那风雨如磐的子夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"默默地嚼着苦味的叶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你执著地追求呀追求，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从不动摇也从未幻灭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白色恐怖中你电贺长征；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"造神大合唱却决不合拍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是一只通体发亮的春蚕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是一张经霜愈艳的红叶！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}